API Reference

This is ShipBlu api reference for merchants who’s have an account on ShipBlu, and would like to integrate their online e-commerce store to our delivery service.

In this api reference we will focus on how you can use our API’s quicly as possible so in some request body we focus on minimum attribute you can write to deal with api without headache.

Our API’s requests divied on six categories:

  1. List
  2. Retreive
  3. Create
  4. Update
  5. Partial update
  6. Delete

Not mandatory each API request has all above six categories. We will show each API response or request body in JSON formate like: { key: value, …. }

key is represent data column name.
value is represent data type.

Let’s start
